snippet.textDisplay:
Bismillah simply means
'In the name of Allah'
Allah is just the arabic equivalent of the the word God or Eshwar or Khudah or Lord...
Bismillah also means
In the name of God or 
In the name of Eshwar
Or In the name of Khudah (depending on the language)
Allah is not a 'muslim God'. Allah is just God. 

Beautiful song and awesomely composed, miraculous performances
